Detailed Description template<typename _Tp, typename _Compare>class __gnu_parallel::_LoserTreePointerUnguardedBase< _Tp, _Compare >
Unguarded loser tree, keeping only pointers to the elements in the tree structure.
No guarding is done, therefore not a single input sequence must run empty. This is a very fast variant.
